item.title: About
item.description: Hello, my name is Nathan, I am known to many simply as “Barta” I am a CS student at the University of Pittsburgh (2020-2025) I am the founder & leader of the Swift Development Branch in PittCSC My interests include: iOS/macOS development Devops / System Design Backend Programming Security (macOS, iOS, and Linux) I have been programming on the iOS platform for 5+ years. I have worked at Leidos Inc, and EZPT as an iOS application developer.
